lead_paragraph: Stand-in captain Sam Cane feels comfortable leading New Zealand against Itay on Saturday even though he has done it only once before and has a relatively inexperienced line-up as the world champions look to bounce back from a rare defeat

headline.print_headline: Cane Comfortable Leading New-Look All Blacks Against Italy
